Package: rasterShade
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper around rayshader package 
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-05-21
Authors@R: c(person("Jan", "Caha", email = "cahik@atlas.cz",
  role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Jan Caha <cahik@atlas.cz>
Description: The package rasterShade is just a wrapper around function in rayshader package. 
The rasterShade package allows using rayshader algorithm directly on spatial data in form of Raster.
The package tries to set "reasonable" default values for parameters in rayshadering algorithm.
These default values are based on real world shadows that can be seen in nature.
